{
  "stem": "12674.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's happening in other places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People kill people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's perfectly all right.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If you're a Jew, you're vermin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it doesn't count.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If something happens to somebody else-- I'm sorry, I don't want to start doing this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "All right, let's stop it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm-- I don't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm getting carried away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother died in 1941, November 1941.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Excuse me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What kind of changes?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived  in the same place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I worked in the same place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Instead of my mother cooking for me, my aunt cooked for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Instead of my mother sleeping in her bed, she had the bed-- the bed.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father slept in the bed now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the bed that he had slept in-- they didn't have a double bed [? that this-- ?] you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he slept in the bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for, for-- we had a Torah in the house for 30 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, we wonder-- you were practically not-- you know, because they said Kaddish there every day for 30 days, and, and-- in a little cupboard they built for that.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and life went on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was religious all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, my father was more religious after the war than he was before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because my father felt that he did not always 100%.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every once in awhile, when he was younger especially, maybe before he married and had children, he was doing certain things that were not according to the book.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm sure he did quite a lot of them, considering who he was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he felt that God had punished him because he did not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I kept saying to him, we, we had-- that was the only-- I adored my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was Daddy's girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He adored me.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
